#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:4
msgid "Installing on Linux"
msgstr "在Linux上安装"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:6
msgid "Check the :doc:`minimum requirements and where to get Blender </getting_started/installing/introduction>`, if you have not done so yet."
msgstr "如果你还不知道的话，先查看 :doc:`最低软硬件需求和下载Blender </getting_started/installing/introduction>`。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:11
msgid "Specific Packages for Distributions"
msgstr "不同发行版的包"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:13
msgid "Some Linux distributions may have on their repositories a specific package for Blender."
msgstr "一些Linux发行版的仓库可能有特定的Blender包 。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:15
msgid ""
"Installing Blender via the distribution's native mechanisms ensures consistency with other packages on the system and may provide other features "
"(given by the package manager), such as listing of packages, update notifications and automatic menu configuration. Be aware, though, that the "
"package may be outdated comparing to the latest official release, or not include some features of Blender. For example, some distributions do not "
"build Blender with CUDA support for licensing reasons."
msgstr ""
"通过发行版自带的安装包安装Blender可以确保与系统中其他包的一致性，并且可以提供其它功能(包管理器提供)，比如包的列表，更新通知以及自动菜单配置。但是要"
"注意的是，这些包可能不是官方最新版，或不包括Blender的某些功能。例如，有些发行版因为许可证的原因未能编译CUDA支持。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:22
msgid ""
"If there is a specific package for your distribution, you may choose what is preferable and most convenient, otherwise, there is nothing wrong "
"with the official binary on `blender.org <https://www.blender.org/download/>`__."
msgstr ""
"如果你使用的发行版有对应的包，自然是再方便不过的了，不过使用 `blender.org <http://www.blender.org/download/>`__ 的官方二进制文件也是没问题的。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:27
msgid "Download from blender.org"
msgstr "从blender.org下载"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:29
msgid "Download the Linux version for your architecture and uncompress the file to the desired location (e.g. ``~/software`` or ``/usr/local``)."
msgstr "下载对应架构的Linux版本并解压缩到所需位置(如： ``~/software`` or ``/usr/local``)。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:32
msgid "Blender can now be launched by double-clicking the executable."
msgstr "现在可以使用双击执行可执行文件启动Blender。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:34
msgid ""
"For easy access, you can configure your system by adding a menu entry or shortcut for Blender and associate and open blend-files with Blender when "
"opening from the File browser. These settings typically belong to the Window Manager (KDE, Gnome, Unity)."
msgstr "为了方便访问， 可以通过添加菜单或Blender快捷方式，并关联blend文件与Blender。这些设置通常位于窗口管理器(KDE, Gnome, Unity)。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:40
msgid "Running from the Terminal"
msgstr "从终端运行"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:42
msgid "To run Blender from the terminal without needing to be in the executable directory, add the extracted folder to the environment ``PATH``."
msgstr "要想不进入可执行文件目录，从终端运行Blender，需要提取该路径并添加到环境 ``路径``。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:45
msgid "Add the following command to ``~/.bashrc`` or ``~/.profile`` pointing to the directory with Blender's binary:"
msgstr "将下面的命令添加到 ``~/.bashrc`` 或 ``~/.profile`` ，路径指向包含Blender二进制文件的目录:"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:53
msgid ""
"If you use daily builds and update Blender frequently, you can link or always rename your folder to 'blender' and use this name for the ``PATH`` "
"environment variable and for keeping the window manager menu up to date."
msgstr ""
"如果你用的是每日编译版，并频繁更新Blender，可以链接或一直重命名指向 'blender' 的文件夹，并使用该名称作为 ``PATH`` 环境变量和坚持更新窗口管理器菜"
"单。"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:59
msgid "Avoiding Alt+Mouse Conflict"
msgstr "避免 Alt+鼠标 冲突"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:61
msgid ""
"Many Window Managers default to :kbd:`Alt-LMB` for moving windows, which is a shortcut that Blender uses to simulate a three button mouse. You can "
"either have this feature disabled :menuselection:`User Preferences --> Input --> Emulate 3 Button Mouse` or you can change the Window Manager "
"settings to use the *Meta* key instead (also called *Super* or *Windows key*):"
msgstr ""
"许多窗口管理器默认使用 :kbd:`Alt-LMB` 移动窗口，但这也是Blender用于模拟三键鼠标的快捷键。可以禁用 :menuselection:`用户界面 --> 输入 --> 模拟三键鼠"
"标` ，或者将窗口管理器快捷键设置替换为 *Meta* 键(也称作 *Super* 或 *Windows 键*):"

#: ../../manual/getting_started/installing/linux.rst:66
msgid "**KDE**: :menuselection:`System Settings --> Window Behavior --> Window Behavior --> Window Actions`, Switch 'Alt' for 'Meta' key."
msgstr "**KDE:** 系统设置 > 窗口行为 > 窗口行为 > 窗口动作 , 切换 'Alt' 为 'Meta' 键。"

